Chinese President Xi Jinping, on January 26, 2022, inspected the post-disaster reconstruction in areas affected by last year's floods in north China's Shanxi Province. He also examined the restoration of farms and efforts to ensure the public has access to heating in winter in Fengnanyuan Village, Shizhuang Town of Huozhou City. He capped things off by wishing villagers in Shanxi a happy Chinese New Year.